snippet.title: Hats Are Not Allowed · Game · Gameplay
snippet.description:
Play this game and more online games like this for free here: https://gamasexual.com/hats-are-not-allowed-game/
Hats Are Not Allowed is a high-quality side-scrolling robot-dueling game. Pick a hat that suits your taste and enter a hostile territory where hats are strictly prohibited.
